title: Ralph Bakshi Animation collection
description:
The 9 full length feature animations directed by Ralph Bakshi between 1972 & 1992 including:

1972 Fritz The Cat
1973 Heavy Traffic
1975 Coonskin
1977 Wizards
1978 The Lord Of The Rings (Fellowship Of The Ring)
1981 American Pop
1982 Hey Good Lookin'
1983 Fire & Ice
1992 Cool World
